abilityArray.title: Zombie Toughness
abilityArray.body: All Zombies you control within 4 clear sight spaces of Liliana get +1#{aotp aotp-defense}.

abilityArray.title: SNUFF OUT
abilityArray.body: Destory target squad creature that has 1 or more damage markers and is within 6 clear sight spaces of Liliana. Use this ability once per turn.

abilityArray.title: Focused Thoughts
abilityArray.body: Look at the top card of your library. You may put that card on the bottom of your library. Use this ability once per turn.

abilityArray.title: Mind Stealer
abilityArray.body: At the end of Jace's turn, you may choose target Planeswalker within    4 clear sight spaces of Jace. Roll     the 20-sided die. If you roll a 16 or higher, you control that Planeswalker and you may use abilities, move,  and attack with the Planeswalker. Afterward, return control of the Planeswalker.

abilityArray.title: Battle Formation
abilityArray.body: Each Rhox Veteran gets +1#{aotp aotp-defense} for each Rhox Veteran you control adjacent to it.

abilityArray.title: Trample
abilityArray.body: While attacking, if a Rhox Veteran would assign enough damage to destroy a defending figure, you may have it assign the rest of its damage to a figure adjacent to the defending figure.

abilityArray.title: Avatar of Justice
abilityArray.body: Gideon gets +X #{aotp aotp-attack} where X is the number of opponents' figures within 2 clear sight spaces of Gideon.

abilityArray.title: Counter Strike
abilityArray.body:
When rolling dice for Gideon on defense against an attack from
an adjacent attacking figure, each excess shield you roll counts as an unblockable hit on the attacking figure.
